sailpoint.object
Class IdentitySnapshot

java.lang.Object
  sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      sailpoint.object.SailPointObject
          sailpoint.object.IdentitySnapshot
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject, sailpoint.tools.xml.XMLReferenceTarget
public class IdentitySnapshot
extends SailPointObject
implements java.lang.Cloneable

A class used to hold historical information about identities. It contains a simplified representation of the full identity cube and can be used to track the roles and exceptional entitlements an identity has had over time.

The createDate of the SailPoint object stores the date of each snapshot.
